        {
            "Type": 1,
            "Data": "Welcome to the RNTYCON 2025: The 1.0 Launch Party - an online event for the community and players of REENTRY.\r\n\r\nAs part of this event, the Flight Plan Mode has been enabled to allow you to try out the concept.\r\n\r\nYou should be familiar with the Apollo Command Module before attempting this mission. I recommend you to complete the Apollo Command Module Academy and completed the Campaign.\r\n\r\nI am trying out three different guided Flight Plan modes and during this event, feel free to give them a try and let me know what you like the most. The main difference is how much the mission will hold your hand.",
            "Value": 0
        },
        {
            "Type": 1,
            "Data": "WORK IN PROGRESS: This is a Reentry - A Space Flight Simulator 2.0 feature currently in its initial development. I am currently trying to make it possible to reach a similar trajectory to the real Mission, but there will be deviations to the exact events such as for example LOS, AOS and lunar terminators. As the game progresses post 1.0 and towards 2.0, I will strive to improve this. The goal of is not to get it exact, but let you get onto a mission close to the real thing.\n\nThe closer I get to 2.0, the more acurate this mission will become.",
            "Value": 0
        },
        {
            "Type": 1,
            "Data": "This mission has been set up to let you fly an Apollo 8 style mission where you start on the PAD for ingress, at the correct time and date for the Apollo 8 launch. The main intent is to let you fly a similar mission without extensive Mission Control / Crew chatter.",
